<---------------------------------Explaination---------------------------------------->

1. Ternary operator
-> isme kuch nhai shamj ne layak ye apne ko ata hi hai fhir bhi revise karne ke liye java notes
jake dhek shakta hai.

2. Switch
-> ye bhi apan ko ata hai to sirf hamare swithStatement wale class me jake ek bar revise kar shakte hai

3. Loops (Do-while, For, For each)
-> do - while loop ek barr to chalega hi bhale hi kuch bhi hojaye kyu ki condtion ham log bad me
lhikte hai .
-> for loop ye shab to ata hi hai
-> forEach bhai iska jake ek barr syntax dhek lena baku ye array ke liye bhot use hota hai.

4. Using break & continue
-> break keyword khai pe bhi ajaye to shamjana ki whia pe wo loop ya to conditional statement end
hora hai.
-> jaha pe continue lhika hai apn ne to continue kya karega wo firse condtion pe jake check karga
and agar condition true hoti hai to particular code ko wapis chala dega .
-> continue skip kardega ek iteration ko kyu ki jaise condition match hoti hai to wo shabse phele i++
pr jata hai and bolta hai ki i ko update karo.

